{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e7868c6567","title":"关于达赖、班禅尽早起程赴京的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af0e74b849","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":3,"articleId":"e7868c6567"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"d8cf396ae1","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，西藏宗教领袖之一。班禅，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，西藏宗教领袖之一。"},{"id":"7689e0394b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共西藏工委1954年6月1日关于达赖为庆祝中印谈判成功宴请我驻藏干部的情况报告上。报告请中央尽早将达赖、班禅等藏族代表去北京开会的时间和人选下达布置。"},{"id":"2a0cb0b342","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、政务院副总理。李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长、中央人民政府民族事务委员会主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f85c1f214c","type":"title","text":"关于达赖、班禅“尽早起程赴京的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567"},{"id":"d8cf396ae1","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓、李维汉同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567"},{"id":"7689e0394b","type":"paragraph","text":"达赖、班禅等藏族代表应尽早起程，九月五日前（最好九月一日前）务必到达北京，请即作部署。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567"},{"id":"2a0cb0b342","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567"},{"id":"1186c89d0e","type":"paragraph","text":"六月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567"}],"page":{"id":"f9f4f70969","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"e7868c6567","start":115,"end":115}}}},"__N_SSG":tru